\begin_layout Itemize
according to CAPM：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
E[R_{i,t}]=R_{f,t}+\beta_{i}(E[R_{m,t}]-R_{f,t})
\]

\end_inset

最常用的计算beta的方法就是run a CAPM regression，the regression specification is:
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
r_{i,t}=\alpha_{i}+\beta_{i}MKT_{t}+\epsilon_{i,t}
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\beta_{i}=\frac{Cov(r_{i,t},MKT_{t})}{Var(MKT_{t})}
\]

\end_inset

其中，
\begin_inset Formula $r_{i,t}$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $MKT_{t}$
\end_inset

都是超额收益率。
\end_layout

