\begin_layout Subsubsection
non-synchronicity
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
to accout for non-synchronicity, Scholes and Williams(1977) propose running
 the series of regressions:
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
r_{i,t}=\alpha_{i}+b_{i}^{-}MKT_{t-1}+\epsilon_{i,t}^{-}
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
r_{i,t}=\alpha_{i}+b_{i}MKT_{t}+\epsilon_{i,t}
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
r_{i,t}=\alpha_{i}+b_{i}^{+}MKT_{t+1}+\epsilon_{i,t}^{+}
\]

\end_inset

and define beta as:
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\beta_{i}^{SW}=\frac{b_{i}^{-}+b_{i}+b_{i}^{+}}{1+2\rho}
\]

\end_inset

where 
\begin_inset Formula $\rho$
\end_inset

 is the first-order serial correlation of the market portfolio's excess
 retrun.
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
由于月度数据基本没有 non-sychronicity 问题，因而，SW法仅适用于daily data
\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
《Betting against beta》中，作者估计beta时，是用
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\beta_{i}=\rho\frac{\sigma_{i}}{\sigma_{M}}
\]

\end_inset

其中，为控制non-synchronous trading的影响，作者在估计相关系数时，对于个股，是用 overlapping 3-day log
 returns:
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
r_{i,t}^{3d}=\sum_{k=0}^{2}ln(1+r_{i,t+k})
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsubsection
infrequent trade bias
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
为避免 非频繁交易(infrequent trade)所导致的估计偏差，Dimson(1979)建议使用：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\beta_{i}^{D}=\sum_{k=-5}^{5}b_{i}^{k}
\]

\end_inset

其中，
\begin_inset Formula $b_{i}^{k}$
\end_inset

来自：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
r_{i,t}=\alpha_{i}+\sum_{k=-5}^{5}b_{i}^{k}MKT_{t+k}+\epsilon_{i,t}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
由于频繁交易的股票并不会引致前述偏差，因而，此种方法不会影响该类股票beta估计的一致性，所以，此方法适用于所有股票
